罩既人<br />\n其實經歷/suffer幾多內心掙扎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52665a487348e9d0890b086ec2ba406630ad8da8","tid":1915882,"uid":41663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"993faf9fd28328b0c24a1b6e59ca2c59a77449ea","tid":1915882,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ede374e962ad3ccd0b4b0245f548584b7c1808bb","tid":1915882,"uid":41663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"135cf672543d0da6ba812904690c6fa7509aaf6b","tid":1915882,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"地主蝦農奴就得<br />\n農奴為脫離地主控制炒賣就唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"唔好變成自己討厭嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"其實好糾結呢個位<br />\n每次交收<br />\n心唸點解有人會五百蚊<br />\n同我買盒例如超快適50枚<br />\n俾我係死唔出街都好都買唔落手<br />\n10蚊一隻n95都已經好唔合理<br />\n仲要係其他口罩<br />\n所以我想像唔到<br />\n同我買罩既人<br />\n其實經歷/suffer幾多內心掙扎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"作為賣家無需太自責 向你買既人出得起呢個錢 又可能家底有番咁上下呢<br />\n<br />\n作為賣家當然有社會責任 標價低啲驚益左班有能力既 咁咪淨係低價賣比啲你相信佢地有需要既人囉<br />\n<br />\n炒黃牛炒波鞋炒錶呢啲都算 唔係必須品 係奢侈品 當口罩變成必須品既時候 出咩價 賣比咩人 我諗你自己應該有答案 不過你都已經散哂貨 想上嚟打個飛機圍爐攞安慰既 就算啦 都冇咩好講"},{"pid":"3ec0d24bb227462c341cf20ae11ea5a1aae430e7","tid":1915882,"uid":170294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"賣得就賣<br />\n正常呀<br />\n<br />\n你去餐廳食飯 3舊水一餐 唔通話人牛排入貨10蚊片 ???"},{"pid":"90597f48ae8496db20d1660cadcc5e3598850d98","tid":1915882,"uid":170294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"你標低價上娘賣 我買左幫你炒高佢<br />\n無意義"},{"pid":"d86ceab07e9ca3fa5d360e361ba505fc1fa31e58","tid":1915882,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"係咪要讚你好撚叻仔好識計數"},{"pid":"c31df81bbf09d7a4f6ddd58e5664eb545698a03f","tid":1915882,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"你賣6，7百出去， 又入返過千口罩？<br />\n如果我有多， 都唔敢賣走<br />\n疫情仲有幾個月"},{"pid":"b1b27c02e29a6c00b551f7362c7f5eeedf042ad8","tid":1915882,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e517bdc017cda71532154ee32370fb79ba5044","tid":1915882,"uid":161883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"兩盒 thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"屋企四老同兩個中學細佬<br />\n都指意曬我啲口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有多我都會捐"},{"pid":"0bf063459ea797633d5097ff5f6a088f4d952f05","tid":1915882,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b27c02e29a6c00b551f7362c7f5eeedf042ad8","tid":1915882,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e517bdc017cda71532154ee32370fb79ba5044","tid":1915882,"uid":161883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"兩盒 thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"屋企四老同兩個中學細佬<br />\n都指意曬我啲口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有多我都會捐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T17:30:07.000Z","msg":"全家六個人（未計我"}]}